Class Component

java.lang.Object
com.cs546.backend.core.components.Component
Direct Known Subclasses:
EmptyComponent, IndustrialComponent, PowerComponent, RailComponent, ResidentialComponent, RetailComponent, RoadComponent
public abstract class Component
extends java.lang.Object
This is the base component that all other components in the city must extend.
